</p></blockquote></glp:note><heading searchtype="COMMENTARY"><edpnum><refpt id="UCPN.UCPR.42-18-10" type="ext"/>[42.18.10] </edpnum><title>Land and Environment Court</title></heading>
<bodytext searchtype="COMMENTARY">
<p>
<text>This rule does not apply to the following classes of proceedings in the Land and Environment Court: Class 1 (environmental planning and protection appeals), Class 2 (local government and miscellaneous appeals and applications) and Class 3 (land tenure, valuation, ratings and compensation matters). It does apply to Class 4 proceedings in that Court see 
<remotelink dpsi="05CC" refpt="UCPN.UCPR.UCPRN05.SCH1" remotekey1="REFPTID" service="DOC-ID">UCPR Sch 1</remotelink>
.</text></p>
</bodytext>
